 Grand Toulouse]]\n|70-70-67-68=275\n|align=center|\u22129\n|4 strokes\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Charles-\u00c9douard Russo]]\n|}\n\n===Other wins (1)===\n*2012 Zurich Open\n\n==Results in major championships==\n{| cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" style=\"font-size: 95%; border: #aaa solid 1px; border-collapse: collapse;text-align:center;\"\n|- style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"\n!align=\"left\"|Tournament\n!2012 !! 2013 !! 2014 !! 2015 !! 2016 !! 2017 !! 2018\n|-\n|align=left|[[Masters Tournament]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|T22\n|T34\n|T43\n|T24\n|-\n|align=left|[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|CUT\n|CUT\n|CUT\n|T16\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|-\n|align=left|[[The Open Championship]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|T64\n|CUT\n|T68\n|CUT\n|T74\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|-\n|align=left|[[PGA Championship]]\n|CUT\n|CUT\n|T15\n|CUT\n|CUT\n|CUT\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|}\n{| cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\" style=\"font-size: 95%; border: #aaa solid 1px; border-collapse: collapse;text-align:center;\"\n|- style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"\n!align=\"left\"|Tournament\n!2019\n|-\n|align=left|[[Masters Tournament]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|-\n|align=left|[[PGA Championship]]\n|style=\"background:#eeeeee;\"|\n|-\n|align=left|[[U.S. Open (golf)|U.S. Open]]\n|76\n|-\n|align=left|[[The Open Championship]]\n|T32\n|}\n<!-- {{legend|yellow|Top 10}} -->\n{{legend|#eeeeee|Did not play}}\nCUT = missed the half-way cut<br />\n\"T\" indicates a tie for a place\n\n===Summary===\n{| class=wikitable style=text-align:center\n!Tournament !! Wins !! 2nd !! 3rd !! Top-5 !! Top-10 !! Top-25 !! Events !! Cuts made\n|-\n|align=left|[[Masters Tournament]]         || 0 || 0 || 0 || 0 || 0 || 2 || 4 || 4\n|-\n|align=left|[[PGA Championship]]           || 0 || 0 || 0 || 0 || 0 || 1 || 6 || 1\n|-\n|align=le